Because the spleen acts for our emergencies.

26:07.340 --> 26:15.910
Supposing a person is extremely speedy; he
just rushes to the bathroom, takes his bath

26:15.910 --> 26:21.210
goes and gets his breakfast and drives on
the way eating his breakfast all the time.

26:21.210 --> 26:25.810
Poor spleen does know how to cope with this
crazy personality.

26:25.810 --> 26:29.080
Because here it is, he’s going in a mad
rush.

26:29.080 --> 26:33.500
In the modern times, you see the traffic is
so bad, they just, they are shouting at the

26:33.500 --> 26:34.500
traffic.

26:34.500 --> 26:36.330
Then there’s a breakfast going on.

26:36.330 --> 26:41.460
All these things are going simultaneously
and poor, this spleen, doesn’t know how

26:41.460 --> 26:48.110
to react and how to cope all the time to these
emergencies, one after another, simultaneously

26:48.110 --> 26:49.730
so many coming up.

26:49.730 --> 26:57.780
So, it gets crazy it loses its control completely
and it starts producing additional blood cells

26:57.780 --> 26:59.580
and blood cells and blood cells.

26:59.580 --> 27:06.960
And when they become too much then they start
flowing on their own, because there is no

27:06.960 --> 27:10.700
relationship left now because of the speediness.

27:10.700 --> 27:14.360
And that’s how Leukaemia has established.

27:14.360 --> 27:18.820
Now leukaemia can be easily cured, very easily
cured.

27:18.820 --> 27:23.760
Because when you put your hand when you are
a Realized soul the energy is flowing.

27:23.760 --> 27:28.560
You just you put your hand on the spleen of
the person, you’ll be surprised that the

27:28.560 --> 27:31.060
spleen settles down because it gets new vitality.

27:31.060 --> 27:37.850
It gets the wisdom from these vibrations,
we can say, from this energy because this

27:37.850 --> 27:42.180
energy is the one that thinks, that cooperates
and organizes.

27:42.180 --> 27:47.170
That’s the one which sorts out also all
kinds of plants and everything.

27:47.170 --> 27:55.020
It is this living energy which when given
to the spleen it becomes wiser: it rests,

27:55.020 --> 27:56.020
it becomes silent.

27:56.020 --> 28:02.730
And also, if you give the person the balance
with your hand, you can make the person much

28:02.730 --> 28:08.620
more relaxed, much more silent within himself.

28:08.620 --> 28:10.140
And that is how you can cure.

28:10.140 --> 28:16.410
And we have, not only that, I have cured of
course nowadays, I don’t cure people much.

28:16.410 --> 28:21.200
There’s a disciple in America and one gentleman
met Me in a village.

28:21.200 --> 28:25.960
He came in his car and he told me that: “My
grandson has gone to America for his treatment

28:25.960 --> 28:29.190
of leukaemia and now they said he’s a gone
case and in 15 days he is going to die.

28:29.190 --> 28:31.920
That’s the certificate”.

28:31.920 --> 28:40.750
So, I told him that: “I’m so busy in the
villages now, you can go back and bring up

28:40.750 --> 28:48.420
this lady she’s there in New York and she’s
an American Sahaja Yogini “.

28:48.420 --> 28:50.090
And he rang her.

28:50.090 --> 28:52.650
She said: “All right, I’ll try to work
it out “.

28:52.650 --> 28:54.800
And she cured him.

28:54.800 --> 29:00.310
The boy came to see Me in London he’s now
back in the school, he’s perfectly all right.

29:00.310 --> 29:02.860
Now people think it’s magical.

29:02.860 --> 29:03.860
It is not!

29:03.860 --> 29:05.040
It’s nothing so great.

29:05.040 --> 29:10.030
Because we take so many things for granted,
every day, if you see the living work of God,

29:10.030 --> 29:11.030
it’s tremendous!

29:11.030 --> 29:15.750
Look at this honey, look at the way the flowers
become fruits.

29:15.750 --> 29:20.790
I mean millions and billions of things we
take it for granted even our evolution from

29:20.790 --> 29:22.430
amoeba to the stage we have come.

29:22.430 --> 29:25.560
We don’t know how we have come, how God
has done it.

29:25.560 --> 29:30.110
It’s done so delicately with such care with
such understanding.

29:30.110 --> 29:35.180
At least we should know that there must be
some meaning when he has brought us to this

29:35.180 --> 29:36.410
level as a human being.

29:36.410 --> 29:37.580
What is the meaning?

29:37.580 --> 29:38.580
Why?

29:38.580 --> 29:39.860
What was the reason?

29:39.860 --> 29:42.470
Why he made us like this?

29:42.470 --> 29:49.590
And just when you discover this meaning spontaneously
automatically this thing gets cured, because

29:49.590 --> 29:52.850
that vitality starts coming to you from the
top.

29:52.850 --> 29:55.520
Now we grow over tensions why?

29:55.520 --> 30:02.630
Because you see, there, with the activity
of these two sides left and right side, we

30:02.630 --> 30:06.530
develop two big balloons in our head.

30:06.530 --> 30:12.660
With the left-side one which is for conditioning
us, which frightens us, gives us fear and

30:12.660 --> 30:18.890
all that, which is our past, we develop an
institution call “superego”.

30:18.890 --> 30:26.180
Such people are all the time under fear, under
danger, or crying, weeping sort of people.

30:26.180 --> 30:29.650
The other side are the people who act.

30:29.650 --> 30:34.550
When they act, they have another by-product
in the head called “ego” which you must

30:34.550 --> 30:36.410
have heard quite a lot.

30:36.410 --> 30:41.530
And this Mr ego is on one side and superego
on another side and once they close down will

30:41.530 --> 30:42.860
become like an eggshell.

30:42.860 --> 30:45.110
You are closed.

30:45.110 --> 30:46.810
You have an “I-ness”.

30:46.810 --> 30:51.050
You are Mr So, you are Mrs So.

30:51.050 --> 30:58.340
Now when this is accumulated there [Agnya]
we feel the tension because either we are

30:58.340 --> 31:04.820
in action or we are in whipping conditions
where we are in inaction.

31:04.820 --> 31:07.700
This tension mounts up in the head and you
feel the tension.

31:07.700 --> 31:10.900
And with this tension you get all sort of
complications.

31:10.900 --> 31:14.120
With the left-side you might get low blood
pressure and all that.

31:14.120 --> 31:16.720
With the right-side you might get high blood
pressure.

31:16.720 --> 31:20.370
Now how do you reduce the tension?

31:20.370 --> 31:22.110
People ask Me how do you reduce the tension?

31:22.110 --> 31:23.650
It’s a very simple thing.

31:23.650 --> 31:25.670
You see, life’s work is extremely simple.

31:25.670 --> 31:27.860
Like your own breathing is so simple!

31:27.860 --> 31:30.510
Have you ever thought about the breathing
that you do?

31:30.510 --> 31:34.950
You don’t read any books you don’t go
anywhere you don’t consult anyone it just

31:34.950 --> 31:36.150
happens to you.

31:36.150 --> 31:41.450
In the same way, it’s such a simple thing
that your tension on the head is because either

31:41.450 --> 31:43.840
you are worried or you are planning something.

31:43.840 --> 31:49.810
You are aggressive or you are taking the aggression;
one of the two.

31:49.810 --> 31:51.280
So, what happens?

31:51.280 --> 31:58.000
Here I say that Christ plays a very big role
in our life because he is placed in that crossing

31:58.000 --> 31:59.560
point if you see.

31:59.560 --> 32:01.570
This is the cross.

32:01.570 --> 32:05.860
When he said on the cross: “It has been
accomplished”.

32:05.860 --> 32:17.060
When he says that the placing of Christ in
that little space of ego and superego is accomplished.

32:17.060 --> 32:26.890
When Christ is awakened through the kindling
of the Kundalini then these two things are

32:26.890 --> 32:27.890
sucked in.

32:27.890 --> 32:31.470
That’s why we say he died for our sins because
the left-side are the sins and the right-side

32:31.470 --> 32:33.850
are the Karmas the action, the ego.

32:33.850 --> 32:35.760
So, he sucks it.

32:35.760 --> 32:40.539
By that suction you are amazed that suddenly
you find there’s a depression here like

32:40.539 --> 32:42.540
a child has.

32:42.540 --> 32:45.920
And you feel the throbbing here.

32:45.920 --> 32:50.180
And after the throbbing you feel the cool
breeze coming out of your head.

32:50.180 --> 32:52.650
From your own head the cool breeze is coming
out.

32:52.650 --> 32:54.280
This Holy Ghost is manifesting herself.

32:54.280 --> 32:55.280
And she’s all around.

32:55.280 --> 33:00.740
Also, you can start feeling in your hands
if your- this centre is all right.

33:00.740 --> 33:02.920
This is what he meant “to be born again”.

33:02.920 --> 33:06.190
Not just to call some people: “All right
now we have a baptism”.

33:06.190 --> 33:10.510
So, the poor child is screaming and you put
your hand on his head and say: “All right,

33:10.510 --> 33:11.510
you’re baptized now”.

33:11.510 --> 33:13.670
That’s artificial, it’s just a drama.

33:13.670 --> 33:16.010
And this kind of drama they do in every religion.

33:16.010 --> 33:17.890
It’s not only in Christianity.

33:17.890 --> 33:21.960
You’ll find even Hindus do the same joke
and everybody has the same joke.

33:21.960 --> 33:27.880
But it’s not true because if there is baptism
there has to be transformation.

33:27.880 --> 33:30.420
And there is no transformation whether you
baptize a child or not.

33:30.420 --> 33:33.700
On the contrary, I have seen some children
they become funny.

33:33.700 --> 33:38.260
Because this is a very precious place, it
is a very holy place [Sahasrara] and anybody

33:38.260 --> 33:44.030
who is not a holy person who is not a sanctified
person places the hand on top of the head

33:44.030 --> 33:47.100
of such any child, he can become even mad.

33:47.100 --> 33:55.040
We had three examples of that kind that people
who got baptism, children who are perfectly

33:55.040 --> 34:01.950
normal but after baptism their eyes started
squinting around and they lost their awareness.

34:01.950 --> 34:07.640
Because the people who put their hands on
this very precious holy place where not themselves

34:07.640 --> 34:08.640
holy.

34:08.640 --> 34:10.720
They didn’t have a clean heart.

34:10.720 --> 34:16.030
And that’s why- this is the centre of the
heart which is there in the Spirit.

34:16.030 --> 34:23.091
And this one [Sahasrara] when it is touched
by someone who has a heart of a stone can

34:23.091 --> 34:25.560
pass bad vibrations satanic vibrations.

34:25.560 --> 34:27.339
People can spoil them.

34:27.339 --> 34:32.129
You have a very great poet in this country-
you had him- was William Blake.

34:32.129 --> 34:34.540
And he said: “A priest cursed on my head”.

34:34.540 --> 34:36.409
And people asked Me: “What it is?”

34:36.409 --> 34:41.710
I said: “The priest must be somebody who
is not such a good man perhaps and he touched

34:41.710 --> 34:42.710
his forehead”.

34:42.710 --> 34:44.030
Because he was a Realized soul.

34:44.030 --> 34:49.190
And he’s written so much about Sahaja Yoga
that nowhere in the world I have seen so much

34:49.190 --> 34:53.280
written about Sahaja Yoga as your great poet
William Blake.

34:53.280 --> 34:57.820
Now when this happens so many other things
can also happen to us.

34:57.820 --> 35:03.840
For example, a person who is very emotional,
for example, the one who is always whipping

35:03.840 --> 35:06.560
crying going to the left-side.

35:06.560 --> 35:12.800
Oh, they are – most of the people feel guilty
that’s the worst disease of the West.

35:12.800 --> 35:17.710
By feeling guilty you get spondylitis, thyroid
all kinds of troubles.

35:17.710 --> 35:18.980
So, no use.

35:18.980 --> 35:21.440
What’s the use to feeling guilty after all?

35:21.440 --> 35:23.970
Or people who believe that “we must suffer”.

35:23.970 --> 35:26.870
Now this I can’t understand at all!

35:26.870 --> 35:29.390
Because Christ has suffered for us.

35:29.390 --> 35:30.650
What more are we going to suffer?

35:30.650 --> 35:32.210
Now he suffered already for us.

35:32.210 --> 35:34.800
Has he left something for us to suffer?

35:34.800 --> 35:38.890
Those people who believe like Jews did believe
in such a thing, they suffered.

35:38.890 --> 35:40.960
We don’t have to suffer at all!

35:40.960 --> 35:44.990
That’s a promise.

35:44.990 --> 35:46.210
He suffered for us.

35:46.210 --> 35:48.970
Only thing, we have to awaken him, that’s
all.

35:48.970 --> 35:55.010
Nor do we have to feel we are very guilty
because if you feel guilty then this left-side

35:55.010 --> 35:56.900
gets caught up [Left Vishudhi].

35:56.900 --> 36:03.050
And it creates a problem for your Realization
first of all and secondly, it might give you

36:03.050 --> 36:04.060
a physical problem.

36:04.060 --> 36:09.630
I’ve seen this is very common with the West
people I don’t know why they should feel

36:09.630 --> 36:10.630
guilty.

36:10.630 --> 36:19.170
One must know that God Almighty is the ocean
of compassion, ocean of love, ocean of forgiveness.

36:19.170 --> 36:24.120
We cannot understand his forgiveness, we cannot
be like him.

36:24.120 --> 36:25.670
And what guilt can we have?

36:25.670 --> 36:32.060
Even the judges on this earth who are just
human beings cannot punish you.

36:32.060 --> 36:34.990
How can that God is going to punish you for
what?

36:34.990 --> 36:39.610
So, we live with myths: “Oh, I should not
have done it, I should not have done it”.

36:39.610 --> 36:44.160
This has come also with our modern life.

36:44.160 --> 36:49.350
For example, if you put your fork and spoon
in this way then you are all right, sophisticated.

36:49.350 --> 36:53.870
If you just put it a little this way: then
you are: “Oh, I should not have done it”.

36:53.870 --> 36:57.620
If you spill the coffee then you are as if
you’d murdered three persons the way you

36:57.620 --> 36:58.620
feel about it.

36:58.620 --> 36:59.660
It is not so.

36:59.660 --> 37:01.490
It’s not so.

37:01.490 --> 37:05.440
In the realm of God what does it matter?

37:05.440 --> 37:06.440
It’s nothing important.

37:06.440 --> 37:09.720
For him, the most important thing is that
you are a human being.

37:09.720 --> 37:15.490
And you must know that you are at the epitome
of the whole creation and that should have

37:15.490 --> 37:19.670
no self-pity about it, no self-pity at all.

37:19.670 --> 37:26.670
But you must have self-confidence that God
has created you with a purpose, that you become

37:26.670 --> 37:31.080
collectively conscious and you see the play
of God’s beauty and his glory.

37:31.080 --> 37:33.590
That’s why he has created you.

37:33.590 --> 37:38.940
Not to feel guilty not to have self-pity and
to cry and weep and always say: “I’m horrible.

37:38.940 --> 37:40.060
I have problems”.

37:40.060 --> 37:46.090
Such people get troubles to themselves while
those are aggressive trouble others.

37:46.090 --> 37:49.950
Both are just the same in the eyes of God
whether you trouble yourself or others, it’s

37:49.950 --> 37:51.900
just the same.

37:51.900 --> 37:59.320
Now this kind of an imbalance that comes within
us can be corrected with the awakening of

37:59.320 --> 38:00.860
Christ within us.

38:00.860 --> 38:05.910
The chanting at this place when he is awakened,
when he is awakened because you are to be

38:05.910 --> 38:06.950
connected with him.

38:06.950 --> 38:10.641
Then is our Lord’s prayer that’s the mantra.

38:10.641 --> 38:18.380
We have to say that he is kept awakened and
that is the chanting we have.

38:18.380 --> 38:25.310
You’ll be amazed after coming to Sahaja
Yoga the Christians who hated the Jews have

38:25.310 --> 38:36.020
understood the importance of Moses because
he resides in this void part, this green circle

38:36.020 --> 38:42.560
and all ten of them who incarnated again and
again reside there.

38:42.560 --> 38:48.490
Now those who are fanatics say, those who
believe that only more Muhammad is the one

38:48.490 --> 38:56.490
or those who believe that only the Moses is
the one or any such funny ideas, they also

38:56.490 --> 38:59.950
suffer physically.

38:59.950 --> 39:06.763
I had a doctor from Iran, about ten years
back I should say, he came to England to see

39:06.763 --> 39:11.390
me and he had a cancer of the stomach.

39:11.390 --> 39:17.400
And I asked him, I said: “Do you believe
that Muhammad is the only one you had?”

39:17.400 --> 39:18.400
“Yes.

39:18.400 --> 39:19.400
I believe in that."

39:19.400 --> 39:20.700
I said: “How can it be?

39:20.700 --> 39:23.580
He himself has said there have been many prophets.

39:23.580 --> 39:25.990
And how can you say that he’s the only one?”

39:25.990 --> 39:28.660
So, he said: “No, no, no.

39:28.660 --> 39:29.701
He was the last.

39:29.701 --> 39:34.120
He was the most modern so I believe in him
and I don’t believe in anybody else”.

39:34.120 --> 39:35.600
I said: “You have to believe in Moses.

39:35.600 --> 39:36.600
“Oh!

39:36.600 --> 39:37.600
That I cannot believe.

39:37.600 --> 39:39.050
These Jews, I can’t believe in them.

39:39.050 --> 39:41.220
I hate the Jews I can’t believe Moses."

39:41.220 --> 39:44.430
I said: “All right, go ahead, if you can’t
believe in him.

39:44.430 --> 39:46.270
Same is Nanaka.

39:46.270 --> 39:50.340
Same is Janaka.

39:50.340 --> 39:51.500
They are the same people again born again.

39:51.500 --> 39:54.230
And the same quality of the Primordial master
is born again.

39:54.230 --> 39:59.210
I said: “All right, go ahead, I cannot cure
you if you are a fanatic you suffer."

39:59.210 --> 40:02.460
So, he went home and he had a bad time.

40:02.460 --> 40:04.110
Doctor said: “You are going to die now”.

40:04.110 --> 40:05.970
So, after eight days his wife brought him
again.

40:05.970 --> 40:11.820
I said: “Now do you believe in it?” he
said: “Yes Mother, I do.

40:11.820 --> 40:13.930
Please, cure me”.

40:13.930 --> 40:15.170
And he got cured.

40:15.170 --> 40:16.790
He’s still alive all right.

40:16.790 --> 40:18.730
Fanaticism has its own respite to.

40:18.730 --> 40:22.890
Fanaticism is real madness I should say to
be fanatical about something.

40:22.890 --> 40:26.960
It’s a mental projection to believe that
somebody belongs to you.

40:26.960 --> 40:31.730
Actually, you have to belong to them and nobody
belongs to you.

40:31.730 --> 40:38.890
This fight of religion imagine when you see
that in this world there are fights going

40:38.890 --> 40:42.860
on in the name of God, in the name of religion,
you’re shocked!

40:42.860 --> 40:50.000
The things that were created for peace, for
bliss and for heavenly abode of human beings

40:50.000 --> 40:56.060
are being used for something that is absolutely
opposite of that.

40:56.060 --> 41:04.030
It’s most surprising how people are believing
into a team to such an extent that they are

41:04.030 --> 41:10.100
just getting monopolized and filthen [unsure]
and they are torturing others.

41:10.100 --> 41:15.320
It could become even very sophisticated like
people who have formed lots of mental projections

41:15.320 --> 41:19.600
you see, they have dogmas, this, that and
they cultivate you every time they have a

41:19.600 --> 41:22.650
lecture and then you believe in it: “Oh,
oui, [yes?] this is this”.

41:22.650 --> 41:25.710
And from your childhood you are told, “you
are like this you are like that”.

41:25.710 --> 41:28.600
Ultimately, what do you find at the end of
life?

41:28.600 --> 41:33.200
Nothing but the same and same and same going
on.

41:33.200 --> 41:39.210
But the principle of religion is to give you
a balance and that doesn’t happen unless

41:39.210 --> 41:41.550
and until this religion is awakened within
you.

41:41.550 --> 41:47.590
Once it is awakened, I don’t have to tell
you that: “You give up your drugs”.

41:47.590 --> 41:49.310
You just give up.

41:49.310 --> 41:51.140
I don’t have to tell you: “Take your alcoholism
out.

41:51.140 --> 41:52.140
” You just do it.

41:52.140 --> 41:53.230
I just don’t tell you.

41:53.230 --> 41:57.360
I don’t say that if you have alcoholism
or anything as a disease it just drops up

41:57.360 --> 41:58.360
automatically.

41:58.360 --> 42:00.860
Even if you want you cannot drink.

42:00.860 --> 42:02.520
You won’t enjoy it at all!

42:02.520 --> 42:08.150
It’s just as a by-product as you get rid
of your troubles.

42:08.150 --> 42:13.590
In the same way, these habits also drop out.

42:13.590 --> 42:20.010
You become independent you become free not
slave of anything because you are the Spirit

42:20.010 --> 42:22.300
which is the freedom within you.

42:22.300 --> 42:25.030
Complete supreme freedom is your Spirit.

42:25.030 --> 42:36.160
Last of all, I will tell you about a horrible
disease, which is the modern disease nowadays,

42:36.160 --> 42:42.090
is the disease of cancer, which is a horrible
thing as people say.

42:42.090 --> 42:49.740
Cancer is caused mostly, which I have seen,
in the people who are left-sided.

42:49.740 --> 42:53.760
Not so much in the right-sided people, those
who are aggressive.

42:53.760 --> 42:56.880
But those who are emotionally ones disturbed
get this trouble.

42:56.880 --> 43:04.650
So far, I have not seen one patient of cancer
who has not been emotionally very much inclined.

43:04.650 --> 43:12.730
It might look, appear that a person is very
aggressive, but if you really go into the

43:12.730 --> 43:19.120
history of a person you will find that he
had a problem, that his mother died, or his

43:19.120 --> 43:24.710
father died early, or some sort of an emotional
problem he developed later on, or a shock

43:24.710 --> 43:29.610
from his wife or a fiancée, from his children
or something like that.

43:29.610 --> 43:35.210
It’s more a case of emotional disturbance.

43:35.210 --> 43:43.360
Now when you find, that a person has a cancer,
on the hands you’ll find that all these

43:43.360 --> 43:45.080
fingers are burning [Shri Mataji shows all
the fingers of Her left hand], sometimes even

43:45.080 --> 43:46.930
these fingers start burning [Shri Mataji shows
fingers of Her right hand].

43:46.930 --> 43:54.190
When it is on a galloping state you put your
hands towards a person who is suffering from

43:54.190 --> 43:59.020
cancer- even doctors might not diagnose it,
they might find it later on – all your fingers

43:59.020 --> 44:00.140
start burning.

44:00.140 --> 44:05.320
You start burning here and here [Shri Mataji
points on the top of the palm near the fingers].

44:05.320 --> 44:06.650
Also, you may start feeling a throbbing here
[Shri Mataji points to the solar plexus].

44:06.650 --> 44:14.340
Of course, throbbing doesn’t mean that a
person has a cancer, but is one of the symptoms.

44:14.340 --> 44:16.330
Now how cancer is caused?

44:16.330 --> 44:17.330
It’s very simple.

44:17.330 --> 44:22.710
And to understand it- it’s better that if
you understand- you will not those things

44:22.710 --> 44:24.740
which are not to be done.

44:24.740 --> 44:30.730
Anything we do into extremes, I mean any emergency
is taking over by this two sides, because

44:30.730 --> 44:33.720
they manifest the sympathetic nervous system.

44:33.720 --> 44:37.370
They act for our sympathetic nervous system
whenever there is an emergency.

44:37.370 --> 44:43.170
For example, a person has a habit, a simple
habit, of say, rubbing his ears, very simple

44:43.170 --> 44:44.170
habit.

44:44.170 --> 44:45.530
He may develop a cancer there.

44:45.530 --> 44:47.310
Because he has overdone it.

44:47.310 --> 44:50.480
An extreme thing he has done is rubbing, rubbing,
rubbing.

44:50.480 --> 44:57.080
So, what happens is that the cells which are
supported by a centre here, for example, it’s

44:57.080 --> 44:58.970
coming from left and right [Shri Mataji forms
a triangle to mime the spinal cord] – and

44:58.970 --> 45:00.080
that’s how a centre is formed.

45:00.080 --> 45:01.820
If you can see all of you.

45:01.820 --> 45:06.520
This is the one through which the medulla
oblongata passes, the spinal cord, this is

45:06.520 --> 45:07.780
the spinal cord.

45:07.780 --> 45:13.630
Now, when there is a pull on right-side or
left-side too much, on the sympathetic nervous

45:13.630 --> 45:17.760
system, then this connection breaks out like
that [Shri Mataji splits the hands].

45:17.760 --> 45:22.900
When it breaks out the connection of the centre
with the whole, because this centre [right

45:22.900 --> 45:25.100
thumb] is supplying the energy, is broken.

45:25.100 --> 45:31.530
When the connection with the whole is broken,
there is no coordination left, there is no

45:31.530 --> 45:32.530
control left.

45:32.530 --> 45:37.170
So, the cells become on their own what we
call malignant.

45:37.170 --> 45:38.440
They start growing on their own.

45:38.440 --> 45:42.230
For example, if their nose develops the cancer,
than nose becomes big.

45:42.230 --> 45:49.340
The rest of the- is smaller and the cells
of the nose start pressing all other organs

45:49.340 --> 45:50.620
in here [on the throat].

45:50.620 --> 45:54.680
And sometimes they may pass into blood and
go to other areas also.

45:54.680 --> 45:59.920
So, these are aggressive cells, malignant
cells are on their own, you cannot control

45:59.920 --> 46:00.920
them.

46:00.920 --> 46:07.420
By some chance, if you could bring them back
in connection with the whole, if you can do

46:07.420 --> 46:09.100
that, cancer can be cured.

46:09.100 --> 46:10.780
It’s as simple as that.

46:10.780 --> 46:15.130
When the Kundalini rises, what she does is,
she awakens the centre.

46:15.130 --> 46:20.670
And when the centre is awakened, it just comes
back to normal and a person becomes normal.

46:20.670 --> 46:22.650
That’s how cancer can be cured.

46:22.650 --> 46:25.110
It is very simple, it’s not so difficult.

46:25.110 --> 46:29.710
Human life we have made it so difficult, actually
it’s not so difficult.

46:29.710 --> 46:37.181
It’s a very simple thing if you understand
the laws of nature and laws of God’s divine

46:37.181 --> 46:38.181
Power.

46:38.181 --> 46:45.910
You can overcome most of your maladies, most
of your problems and you’ll reside in the

46:45.910 --> 46:47.440
kingdom of God.

46:47.440 --> 46:54.000
Now, there are so many other diseases which
I don’t want to refer now because I have

46:54.000 --> 46:55.680
tell to you the physical side.

46:55.680 --> 46:58.870
And the mental side is the left side as I
told you.

46:58.870 --> 47:04.420
Also, on the left side is another disease,
is multiple sclerosis.

47:04.420 --> 47:07.810
I saw a very good television show the other
day.

47:07.810 --> 47:10.770
It was put up by some doctors.

47:10.770 --> 47:18.760
And they said that in ourselves there is an
area which is built in from our creation,

47:18.760 --> 47:21.330
means the collective subconscious.

47:21.330 --> 47:24.540
That’s what we call it.

47:24.540 --> 47:30.220
And there are proteins which they call protein
58, protein 52 or something like that.

47:30.220 --> 47:35.040
They enter into our being and trigger the
cancer.

47:35.040 --> 47:40.460
So that shows what we have said, that there
are dead within us.

47:40.460 --> 47:46.800
On the left-hand side is the subconscious
and then the collective subconscious.

47:46.800 --> 47:52.420
And when you enter into the collective subconscious,
anyone of this spirits can catch hold of you.

47:52.420 --> 47:57.410
Once they catch hold of you, you are liable
to any of these diseases.

47:57.410 --> 48:02.930
Specially I have seen if there is a possessed
person – of course they become mad, they

48:02.930 --> 48:05.470
get epilepsy, all this are possessed people.

48:05.470 --> 48:10.130
Epilepsy can be cured; we have someone here
who had epilepsy of the worse type.

48:10.130 --> 48:13.320
She is cured completely.

48:13.320 --> 48:17.110
And all such mental troubles, depression,
can be cured.

48:17.110 --> 48:19.010
Not difficult at all.

48:19.010 --> 48:23.650
But one must know, that if you are possessed
you must really work it out and see to it,

48:23.650 --> 48:26.730
that it goes away from you and you become
yourself.

48:26.730 --> 48:29.270
Because when you are the other, you don’t
know what’s happening to you.

48:29.270 --> 48:35.710
Now this affliction when it comes to you,
there is another horrible disease called multiple

48:35.710 --> 48:38.060
sclerosis which comes up.

48:38.060 --> 48:43.950
I have seen so far there three cases in England
of multiple sclerosis which have been cured

48:43.950 --> 48:45.290
by Sahaja Yoga.

48:45.290 --> 48:48.950
All of them had either the wife or the husband
possessed.

48:48.950 --> 48:51.160
Can you imagine?

48:51.160 --> 48:53.360
It’s something surprising.

48:53.360 --> 48:56.130
We do not know these things are so important.

48:56.130 --> 49:02.050
These are very important things and that’s
why all these people come on this earth said,

49:02.050 --> 49:04.820
that you lead a clean life.

49:04.820 --> 49:07.840
And a sensible married life.’

49:07.840 --> 49:14.900
It is not permitted to have an adulteress
life in any religion whatsoever, because adulteress

49:14.900 --> 49:20.950
life brings forth all kinds of problems of
the sex spoiling the last chakra.

49:20.950 --> 49:27.730
People can become impotent or overexcited,
could become suffering from all the troubles

49:27.730 --> 49:32.760
of this centre, which you know are diseases
which are kept as secrets.

49:32.760 --> 49:40.400
So, one has to lead a very clean wonderful
married life, because marriage is supported

49:40.400 --> 49:42.630
and sanctioned by the collective.

49:42.630 --> 49:46.030
It is sanctioned by God almighty.

49:46.030 --> 49:50.280
So, that kind of a life, that kind of a sexual
life, is a sensible one.

49:50.280 --> 49:52.270
One should not get a shock out of it.

49:52.270 --> 49:55.310
When I say this in the west, people really
don’t like it.

49:55.310 --> 49:56.630
But I’m your mother.

49:56.630 --> 49:59.050
I have to tell you the truth.

49:59.050 --> 50:01.660
Even whatever you have done is done – finished,
doesn’t matter.

50:01.660 --> 50:04.430
But now come to your sanity.

50:04.430 --> 50:10.970
Because there are all these horrible satanic
diseases waiting just to gulp you down.

50:10.970 --> 50:14.450
Apart from diseases such a person creates
a problem for children.

50:14.450 --> 50:16.141
He creates a problem for the whole society.

50:16.141 --> 50:17.400
The whole society topples down.

50:17.400 --> 50:24.070
If they do not respect the marriage, if the
woman becomes aggressive and try to sort of

50:24.070 --> 50:27.770
replace men – they cannot do it, they are
woman.

50:27.770 --> 50:29.180
Men are man, woman are woman.

50:29.180 --> 50:31.990
But that doesn’t mean that somebody is going
to suppress.

50:31.990 --> 50:34.310
They are equal, no doubt, but not similar.

50:34.310 --> 50:37.450
This is a simple point we don’t understand.

50:37.450 --> 50:41.369
They woman is to be respected, but she has
to be respectable.

50:41.369 --> 50:47.310
And she has to be respected, because she is
one who is the power behind the man.

50:47.310 --> 50:51.120
If we understand all these simple things of
life, the life becomes very beautiful.

50:51.120 --> 50:53.610
How we have to respect our elders.

50:53.610 --> 50:55.080
How we have to respect everyone.

50:55.080 --> 50:58.100
The respect itself is gone from the modern
times.

50:58.100 --> 51:02.119
People have accepted themselves as something
you see ‘what’s wrong’ business.

51:02.119 --> 51:04.150
There is no respect for anything whatsoever.

51:04.150 --> 51:08.320
I mean the way they bark at each other; one
doesn’t understand how human beings have

51:08.320 --> 51:13.680
become now dogs or what have they become the
way they start barking at each other.

51:13.680 --> 51:20.000
The whole system goes out of gear when we
become too much materialistic also, because

51:20.000 --> 51:26.510
the matter makes us absolutely a dead matter
also.

51:26.510 --> 51:31.460
But I’m not saying that you have to give
up anything.

51:31.460 --> 51:32.480
What do you give up?

51:32.480 --> 51:38.070
You don’t give up anything because if you
have not taken anything into you, if you do

51:38.070 --> 51:41.670
not cling anything to anything, what do you
give up?

51:41.670 --> 51:47.070
Like this people Hare Rama came to Me and
they saw Me in My house and of course I mean,

51:47.070 --> 51:48.280
we live very well.

51:48.280 --> 51:53.250
Perhaps they thought it was too much for a
saint like Me to life in all these luxuries.

51:53.250 --> 51:57.670
And they started saying: ‘Mother, You are
living in this fashion and how people call

51:57.670 --> 51:58.840
You a saint.

51:58.840 --> 52:00.400
I said: All right.

52:00.400 --> 52:03.000
Now, you talk of Lord Krishna, isn’t it?

52:03.000 --> 52:08.410
Now in this house or one My body anywhere
you find anything equal to the dust of the

52:08.410 --> 52:11.820
feed of Lord Krishna, you take it away.

52:11.820 --> 52:13.530
Anything, but must equal!

52:13.530 --> 52:14.820
‘ That’s one thing.

52:14.820 --> 52:17.761
They looked around and they could find anything.

52:17.761 --> 52:19.770
I said: ‘What have you given up?

52:19.770 --> 52:20.780
Stones?

52:20.780 --> 52:21.780
Ashes?

52:21.780 --> 52:23.200
What is there to give up?‘

52:23.200 --> 52:29.510
When you just see the whole thing as a drama,
when you are not clinging on anything, what

52:29.510 --> 52:30.510
is there to give up?

52:30.510 --> 52:32.650
In Sahaja Yoga we don’t believe in false
asceticism at all.

52:32.650 --> 52:37.010
Be believe in the real asceticism which comes
from within.

52:37.010 --> 52:38.760
Where a person gives.

52:38.760 --> 52:42.390
Where a person enjoys matter in giving others.

52:42.390 --> 52:48.110
We don’t believe in this kind of a falsehood
that you wear a certain type of cloth or you

52:48.110 --> 52:53.390
have a nunnery or this judo-sannyasis going
around.

52:53.390 --> 52:54.390
None of these things.

52:54.390 --> 52:57.880
You have to lead a very normal life in the
centre.

52:57.880 --> 53:01.060
All the great saints of India were married
and had children.

53:01.060 --> 53:03.890
Except for some people like Buddha who died
very early.

53:03.890 --> 53:07.080
He had to take a sannyasa because of His work.

53:07.080 --> 53:14.250
Then we had people like also we can say Kabira,
Nanaka – all of them were married people.

53:14.250 --> 53:18.490
And nobody talked of this extreme nature that
you have to give up everyone.

53:18.490 --> 53:19.791
Such people can be very, very dangerous.

53:19.791 --> 53:23.340
They can be very hot tempered.

53:23.340 --> 53:27.040
They can be so hot tempered that you cannot
just face them.

53:27.040 --> 53:32.100
Because marriage makes you very normal to
come in the centre.

53:32.100 --> 53:36.860
In this life, in this married life you are
going to receive the blessings of God.

53:36.860 --> 53:38.760
There is no abnormity needed.

53:38.760 --> 53:44.470
Actually, we become extremely normal when
you get your realization.

53:44.470 --> 53:47.970
Of course, some of these ideas may not appeal
to you.

53:47.970 --> 53:52.690
But you can see for yourself, whatever I say
is true or not?

53:52.690 --> 53:55.110
After Realization, you become a different
person.

53:55.110 --> 53:59.460
Your priorities change, you become such a
beautiful person because you start giving.

53:59.460 --> 54:02.290
The whole thing starts flowing from you.

54:02.290 --> 54:05.940
Because you become the light and the light
starts flowing from you.

54:05.940 --> 54:15.890
And then you understand and assume your powers,
powers of your Spirit and you enjoy this compassionate

54:15.890 --> 54:16.890
flow.

54:16.890 --> 54:21.560
And all the things look very different, the
whole life changes.

54:21.560 --> 54:27.790
This has to happen to the whole world if you
bring peace and sanity, if you have to save

54:27.790 --> 54:30.030
this creation, we have to do this.

54:30.030 --> 54:34.330
Actually, the divine is more anxious than
anybody else to do it because the creation

54:34.330 --> 54:37.040
will be lost if human beings are lost.

54:37.040 --> 54:43.410
So, those who are people who are seeking should
understand their responsibility that they

54:43.410 --> 54:45.810
have to become the spirit.

54:45.810 --> 54:50.700
And after becoming the spirit they have to
manifest the powers of their spirit.

54:50.700 --> 54:53.960
These are their own powers which they manifest.

54:53.960 --> 54:56.690
Only they have to know how to work it out.

54:56.690 --> 54:59.940
It’s very simple as I said.

54:59.940 --> 55:06.080
And to have it is the best way to understand
it.

55:06.080 --> 55:08.790
May God bless you all.

55:08.790 --> 55:14.650
I would like to have some questions from new
people because today is the first lecture

55:14.650 --> 55:15.740
here, but for a short time.

55:15.740 --> 55:17.220
