55:19.980 --> 55:25.900
I’m here to do good to you, not to do any
harm to you whatsoever, take it from Me.

55:25.900 --> 55:31.700
So, be kind to Me and ask Me questions which
are good for you and for everybody else, because

55:31.700 --> 55:37.000
they are all just waiting for their Realization
which should not also spoil their chances

55:37.000 --> 55:38.030
and delay the matter.

55:38.030 --> 55:42.910
So, I would request you to ask Me questions
which are sensible related to the subject

55:42.910 --> 55:46.970
and I’ll be very happy to answer them because
certainly when you get your Realization you

55:46.970 --> 55:51.060
will find your mind will peep out: ‘Oh,
you didn’t ask this question to mother.’

55:51.060 --> 55:58.530
I’m sorry I have been speaking now every
day and last month I was too [?].

55:58.530 --> 56:05.520
Everyday there was a speech on, so little
bit there is a strain on My throat, doesn’t

56:05.520 --> 56:06.520
matter.

56:06.520 --> 56:10.110
Can I request you to ask Me questions please?

56:10.110 --> 56:14.340
Thank you.

