It’s your freedom.

57:26.450 --> 57:27.540
It’s your freedom!

57:27.540 --> 57:31.920
Whether you want to cooperate or not, but
sometimes people don’t cooperate, then I

57:31.920 --> 57:32.970
can’t help it.

57:32.970 --> 57:38.770
It’s noting great is to be done but few
things that have to be followed if you cooperate

57:38.770 --> 57:44.880
with Me, of course it can be done without
of course any charges, anything, it just works

57:44.880 --> 57:45.880
out.

57:45.880 --> 57:46.880
Yes.

