58:17.180 --> 58:18.369
Because you are within Me.

58:18.369 --> 58:26.280
When you start everyone – you’re feeling
another person within yourself we really don’t

58:26.280 --> 58:27.280
help anyone.

58:27.280 --> 58:29.200
There is no question of charity.

58:29.200 --> 58:31.390
It’s question of my saving myself.

58:31.390 --> 58:33.060
All right?

