Woman: I’d like your help too, please.

58:38.910 --> 58:42.810
Shri Mataji: What is it?

58:42.810 --> 58:46.180
Woman: I’d like your help too.

58:46.180 --> 58:47.460
Shri Mataji: What did she say, Gavin?

