Gavin: She say’s also that she would like
to have your help.

58:51.870 --> 58:54.840
Shri Mataji: All of you.

58:54.840 --> 58:59.840
All of you are going to be helped in a way
if you say call it ‘help’, but I don’t

58:59.840 --> 59:01.470
like the word ‘help’ much.

59:01.470 --> 59:02.890
It’s your own.

59:02.890 --> 59:04.310
It’s your own.

59:04.310 --> 59:08.840
Just like if you go to a banker for example.

59:08.840 --> 59:12.770
Then you say: ‘Can I have my check cashed?’

59:12.770 --> 59:13.770
All right?

